{"tid":1857902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★無視肺炎！】愉景灣單位逆市破頂創新高！！","createTime":"2020-02-02T11:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T04:55:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"40e7b610fa7d270702f08c4ea2e4d9a126f55479","tid":1857902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"香港興業國際(00480)銷售及市務助理總經理陳秀珍表示，旗下愉景灣意堤過去兩日(2月1日及2日)共售出3個單位。其中以招標形式售出的5座18樓A室，為特色天池單位，屬三房連雙套房間隔，實用面積1,425方呎，設1,425方呎私人平台連按摩池，成交價3,600萬元，呎價25,263元，單位成交價及呎價均創項目新高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200202/bkn-20200202174345000-0202_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200202%2Fbkn-20200202174345000-0202_00842_001.html&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9B3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=b11159fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200202/bkn-20200202174345000-0202_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"290ea6e948051bb482536427b6e9f221eb129bab","tid":1857902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e51e64bb47a5e239d745d839f8bea762ae0b90","tid":1857902,"uid":32250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd738f4d0cf569cfe075bacbba0a877cfc8a6efc","tid":1857902,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0